{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c650e2b4da","title":"接见李宗仁先生及其夫人的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8cf9b2625f","index":0,"year":1965,"month":7,"day":27,"articleId":"c650e2b4da"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee2c9ae5ba","type":"title","text":"接见李宗仁先生及其夫人的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"37041f6664","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席同李宗仁先生及其夫人热烈握手。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"f3298eb7be","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：你们回来，很好，欢迎你们。李宗仁先生说：我们回来后都为祖国的强大感到高兴。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"facaf2a4d7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：祖国是比过去强大了一些，但还不很强大，我们至少还得再建设二三十年才能真正强大起来。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"8017c8a5df","type":"paragraph","text":"李宗仁先生对毛主席说：在海外的许多人士都怀念祖国，他们渴望回到祖国来。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"743e77f52a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：跑到海外的，凡是愿意回来，我们都欢迎。他们回来我们都以礼相待。毛主席建议李宗仁先生到全国各地去看看。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"f0b25136a2","type":"paragraph","text":"今天同时被接见的还有陈思远先生。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"},{"id":"7c209cea49","type":"paragraph","text":"接见后，毛泽东主席和江青同志设宴招待李宗仁先生和夫人郭德洁女士，以及陈思云先生。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da"}],"page":{"id":"2461eef7b7","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"c650e2b4da","start":448,"end":449}}}},"__N_SSG":true}